### Install
```bash
$ [sudo] pip install vlc
```

### Examples
```python
>>> vlc.open('path/to/video.avi')
>>> vlc.path
'path/to/video.avi'
>>> vlc.duration
4800

>>> vlc.pause()
>>> vlc.play()
>>> vlc.playing
True
```

fullscreen
```python
>>> vlc.fullscreen.enter()
>>> vlc.fullscreen.detect()
True
>>> vlc.fullscreen.exit()
```

volume
```python
>>> vlc.volume.change(50)  # 0..512
>>> vlc.volume.get()
50
```

time
```python
>>> vlc.time.change(10)
>>> vlc.time.get()
10
```

process
```python
>>> vlc.pid()
42
>>> vlc.kill()  # vlc.kill() or vlc.quit()
```

`vlc.tell(applescript)` - `tell application "VLC"`
```python
>>> vlc.tell('path of current item')
'path/to/video.avi'
```

